{"tid":685091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮貿易顧問：已做好準備應對中國報復","createTime":"2018-05-31T06:46:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T02:33:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c765d7331008d4e4ddc51ac1a88e920c0b8be3cc","tid":685091,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T06:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2080000/2084498/no002_1024_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2080000%2F2084498%2Fno002_1024_1024_1024.jpg&h=af5a07b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國財長姆欽（Steven Mnuchin）上周日（20日）表示中美貿易戰已經停火，被視為鷹派的白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅（Peter Navarro）批評姆欽的說法是「令人遺憾的」，並指中美兩國仍然有紛爭未平息。<br />\n<br />\n指貿易糾紛未平息 新一輪關稅措施是歷史性決定<br />\n<br />\n納瓦羅昨日在電台節目中表示，我們和中國有一直存在貿易糾紛，就這麼簡單。他說，因為北美自由貿易協定（NAFTA）等協議和中國加入世界貿易組織（WTO），「我們很久之前就輸掉貿易戰了」。<br />\n<br />\n納瓦羅對中美貿易議題立場強硬，他批評姆欽的說法，認為不應該把中美貿易糾紛形容為貿易戰，因為美方的措施只是回應中國連串不平等貿易行為；至於是否擔心中國報復美國農產品，他指美國已經「做好一切準備」，應對中國可能的報復。<br />\n<br />\n對於白宮29日突然宣布採取對中國新一波的關稅措施，納瓦羅稱此為「歷史性決定」，目的是維護「美國國家安全」及保護美國的知識產權，重點在阻止中國通過「中國製造2025」計劃，試圖主導全球高科技行業的野心，以及遏制中國竊取美國「高科技皇冠上的明珠」。<br />\n<br />\n白宮回應淡化姆欽發言：有最終決定權的是總統<br />\n<br />\n美國白宮秘書桑德斯（Sarah Sanders）今天被問到有關納瓦羅的回應時，試圖淡化姆欽的發言，她指姆欽不是說「無限期」停火，又指對貿易事務有最終決定權的是總統特朗普，並表示「當他下了決定時，我們就負責宣布，而這正是現階段發生的事」。<br />\n<br />\n上周日，美國政府宣布商務部部長羅斯將會率領代表團，前往中國進行談判，而昨天美國表示計劃對中國總值500億美元的進口貨品徵收25%關稅，並對中國投資高科技產業作出新限制。<br />\n<br />\n美國經貿代表團昨日已抵達北京，並將與中方磋商落實貿易聯合聲明共識。《華爾街日報》引述消息指，美國加徵關稅的舉動或會擾亂會談氣氛，若今次商談沒有結果，羅斯有可能取消訪華。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2084498/%E5%8F%8D%E9%A7%81%E4%BC%91%E6%88%B0%E8%AB%96%20%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F%EF%BC%9A%E5%B7%B2%E5%81%9A%E5%A5%BD%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A0%B1%E5%BE%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2084498%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%25A7%2581%25E4%25BC%2591%25E6%2588%25B0%25E8%25AB%2596%2520%25E7%2599%25BD%25E5%25AE%25AE%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%2595%258F%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25B0%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25BE%25A9&d=GnWKmyyN4rJLgsDKGmBCiIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=dc50cce8\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2084498/%E5%8F%8D%E9%A7%81%E4%BC%91%E6%88%B0%E8%AB%96%20%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F%EF%BC%9A%E5%B7%B2%E5%81%9A%E5%A5%BD%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A0%B1%E5%BE%A9</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49391c728ce7dbcde373b99454663dbdd123122","tid":685091,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T15:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc48333565f5a555ecf2a76aa19767e6f45a348","tid":685091,"uid":41245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T17:37:24.000Z","msg":"識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話貿易戰停火<br />\n但係照有關稅<br />\n因為唔好將美中貿易爭議形容為貿易戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似似曾相識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那用唔少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598d25e405f1267620f0cffcf7c65aebcb101449","tid":685091,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbc48333565f5a555ecf2a76aa19767e6f45a348","tid":685091,"uid":41245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T17:37:24.000Z","msg":"識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話貿易戰停火<br />\n但係照有關稅<br />\n因為唔好將美中貿易爭議形容為貿易戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似似曾相識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那用唔少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T17:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ca07eeb97d41fdcc2d3dfe6bc1d3637bd9e975","tid":685091,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T02:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a7fd28149ccf9d0c5fd8a7b0655966137898f4","tid":685091,"uid":182192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T02:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb8c208ced6fdaad32c2274a3c2d5c4e899a8bed","tid":685091,"uid":2521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T02:33:28.000Z","msg":"美國：中國想贏？冇問題，我地輸左啦...但係我地會做野黎平衡返輸左ge地方<br />\n<br />\n中國：咱們勝利了"}]}